  "recipientNPC": null,
  "recipientName": "Ben",
  "text": "achievement? team work with Mario, it was a cool moment. i feel like it could bring us closer? maybe teamwork could be a feature.\ni do wish i could heal more, felt hopeless, but then again we didnt ask about healing, so maybe something in the future so i wont feel so repeatable (i used frost ball 3 times esentially), i could heal.\nthe brothers were not really giving anything about the conflict it felt aimless to talk to them so we could only really fight, which went well eventually so idk.",
